{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-700-the-os-x-app-sandbox"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Discover how you can use App Sandbox to protect your app’s users from unintentional bugs or deliberate attempts to compromise security. Understand sandboxing’s security goals, how applications and their data are isolated from each other, and how to express the resources your application needs. Learn about new App Sandbox features in Mountain Lion and how to adopt them for your app to meet the Mac App Store Guidelines.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"title":"The OS X App Sandbox","roleHeading":"WWDC12","role":"sampleCode"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"article","sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/700\/","type":"reference"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-700-The-OS-X-App-Sandbox","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"WWDC12.jpeg":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC12.jpeg","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12.jpeg"}]},"WWDCNotes.png":{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","t